{"data":[{"date":"09:18 12/08","title":"HLV Inter th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 mang Modric r\u1eddi Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/12/hlv-luciano-spalletti-khong-tin-inter-milan-co-luka-modric.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Luciano Spalletti kh\u00f4ng tin Inter Milan c\u00f3 Luka Modric. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia r\u1ea5t khao kh\u00e1t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia nh\u01b0ng m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 v\u1ebb kh\u00f4ng di\u1ec5n ra nh\u01b0 h\u1ecd mong \u0111\u1ee3i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Inter mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Modric</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tu\u1ed5i g\u1ea7n 33, Luka Modric v\u1eabn th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Anh l\u00e0 m\u1eaft x\u00edch quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap Real Madrid gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League m\u00f9a th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp. C\u00f9ng \u0110T Croatia d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018, Modric ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u01b0a tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Real t\u1eadp trung, Modric \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi m\u1eddi ch\u00e0o. Trong \u0111\u00f3, nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Inter Milan, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n b\u1ed5 sung l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau khi gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Luciano Spalletti kh\u00f4ng tin Inter Milan c\u00f3 Luka Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Luciano Spalletti kh\u00f4ng tin Inter Milan c\u00f3 Luka Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/HLV-Luciano-Spalletti-khong-tin-Inter-Milan-co-Luka-Modric-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Inter quan t\u00e2m Modric c\u1ee7a Real</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nInter s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 g\u1ea7n g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 Modric \u0111ang l\u0129nh t\u1ea1i Real (10 tri\u1ec7u Euro/ m\u00f9a). H\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng d\u00e0nh cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u n\u00e0y b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m thay cho giao k\u00e8o hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 2 n\u0103m l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Spalletti bi quan</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi \u0111\u1ec3 Mateo Kovacic t\u1edbi Chelsea, Real Madrid \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Modric. H\u1ecd t\u00ednh t\u0103ng m\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3i ng\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Tottenham k\u00fd v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. \u0110\u1ebfn HLV Luciano Spalletti kh\u00f4ng tin Inter Milan c\u00f3 Luka Modric.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Spalletti\" title=\"HLV Spalletti\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/hlv-luciano-spalletti-khong-tin-inter-milan-co-luka-modric.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Spalletti kh\u00f4ng tin Inter Milan c\u00f3 Luka Modric</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Atletico Madrid \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup, Spalletti v\u1eabn \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Inter khi theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Modric. \u201cVi\u1ec7c Modric \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd t\u1edbi Inter l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho d\u1ef1 \u00e1n c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i\u201d, HLV n\u00e0y n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Sky Sport Italia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTh\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0ng b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ch\u00fang ta c\u00f9ng ch\u1edd xem. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 Modric s\u1ebd gia nh\u1eadp, b\u1edfi Real v\u1eabn tr\u00f4ng c\u1eady nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu Modric t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Inter s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ngay \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Inter Milan tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-dam-phan-mua-mauro-icardi-180-194183.html\">B\u1ecb nh\u0103m nhe c\u01b0\u1edbp Modric, Real ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f2n Inter</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/luka-modric-tinh-roi-real-sang-inter-milan-180-193950.html\">V\u00ec \u201cmi\u1ebfng b\u00e1nh\u201d b\u00e9o b\u1edf n\u00e0y, Modric t\u00ednh b\u1ecf Real sang Inter</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/inter-quyet-tam-chieu-mo-bang-duoc-luka-modric-176-193748.html\">Inter quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Luka Modric</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-ra-gia-modric-cho-cac-doi-tac-180-192606.html\">V\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y, M.U v\u00e0 Inter c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang Modric r\u1eddi Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/hlv-spalletti-phat-bieu-ve-chuyen-nhuong-inter-176-192251.html\">HLV Inter Milan mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5386","checkdouble":"194295"},{"date":"11:02 12/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh PSG vs Caen 02h00 ng\u00e0y 13/8 (Ligue 1 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/nhan-dinh-psg-vs-caen-02h00-ngay-138-ligue-1-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>PSG vs Caen l\u00fac 02h00 ng\u00e0y 13/8 (V\u00f2ng 1 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Ph\u00e1p Ligue 1 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh PSG vs Caen 02h00 ng\u00e0y 138 Ligue 1 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh PSG vs Caen 02h00 ng\u00e0y 138 Ligue 1 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/PSG-vs-Caen.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">PSG vs Caen</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span>PSG vs Caen: 5-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Trong khi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 Lyon, Monaco, Nice hay Marseille \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ea3y m\u00e1u l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y th\u00ec PSG v\u1eabn \u0111ang tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 v\u00e0 gia ta t\u0103ng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra CLB n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Parc Des Princes.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o PSG sa th\u1ea3i Unai Emery v\u00e0 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Thomas Tuchel c\u0169ng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1o n\u00ean 1 phong c\u00e1ch v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi. \u0110\u00f4i khi ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t tinh th\u1ea7n v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Paris c\u0169ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi b\u1ed9 3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar, Cavani v\u00e0 Mbappe, h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a PSG \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. C\u1ea3 3 ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y v\u1eeba ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u1edf World Cup v\u1eeba qua, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Tuchel khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 gi\u00fap PSG l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. V\u00e0 \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u \u00f4ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Monaco 4-0 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh Si\u00eau c\u00fap Ph\u00e1p tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Th\u00e2m Quy\u1ebfn, Trung Qu\u1ed1c. \u1ede gi\u1ea3i qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i, qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh danh hi\u1ec7u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chinh ph\u1ee5c Champions League, Tuchel c\u1ea7n gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u01a1n tru v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i \u1edf Ligue 1. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Caen \u0111\u00eam nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, PSG nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Mbappe v\u00e0 Cavani, nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi Neymar v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i Caen v\u1edbi 1 t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eadm. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 x\u1ea3y ra b\u1edfi Caen \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u1edf 10 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 7 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1 nh\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar c\u0169ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m thi \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi sau 1 k\u1ef3 World Cup kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n c\u1ef1u sao Barca ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n nghi\u00eam t\u00fac, PSG s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 1 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ef0C L\u01af\u1ee2NG<br>\r\n- PSG: V\u1eafng Layvin Kurzawa, Marco Verratti v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n  th\u01b0\u01a1ng; kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Presnel Kimpembe, Kylian Mbappe v\u00e0 Edinson  Cavani c\u00f2n b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf.<br>\r\n- Caen: V\u1eafng Baissama Sankoh v\u00e0 Jonathan Gradit do ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPHONG \u0110\u1ed8 vs \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- PSG kh\u00f4ng thua 15/16 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Ligue 1.<br>\r\n- 4 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a PSG \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 t\u1eeb 4 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean.<br>\r\n- Caen ch\u01b0a th\u1eafng trong 10 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, trong \u0111\u00f3 thua t\u1edbi 7.<br>\r\n- PSG th\u1eafng 4/6 l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p Caen g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t t\u1eeb 2 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5385","checkdouble":"194304"},{"date":"11:10 12/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Lyon vs Amiens 20h00 ng\u00e0y 12/8 (Ligue 1 2017/18)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/12/nhan-dinh-lyon-vs-amiens-20h00-ngay-128-ligue-1-201718.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Lyon vs Amiens l\u00fac 20h00 ng\u00e0y 12/8 (V\u00f2ng 1 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Ph\u00e1p Ligue 1 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Lyon vs Amiens 20h00 ng\u00e0y 128 Ligue 1 201718 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Lyon vs Amiens 20h00 ng\u00e0y 128 Ligue 1 201718 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/lyon-amiens.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Lyon vs Amiens</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> Lyon vs Amiens: 4-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>\u1ede tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Ligue 1 m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Amiens t\u1eebng g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua s\u00e1t n\u00fat Lyon 1-2 trong t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eabn b\u00e0n ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 9. Ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi t\u1eadn ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 79, Houssem Aouar m\u1edbi \u0111em v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1 cho Lyon. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu Gael Kakuta \u0111\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng qu\u1ea3 11m \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 89 th\u00ec ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc Aouar c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap cho m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec3m cho Lyon hay kh\u00f4ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u m\u00e0 d\u00f9 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t, nh\u01b0ng Amiens \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c hay v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Lyon.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n9 th\u00e1ng sau, hai \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1ea1i g\u1eb7p nhau. Nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. HLV Bruno Genesio \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 cho Lyon b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. C\u00f2n nh\u1edb m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a M\u00e3nh s\u01b0 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u0103ng c\u01a1 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean v\u00e0 b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed1i s\u1ee9c \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u01b0\u1edbc r\u00fat, khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u00fa b\u0103ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch theo th\u00f3i quen v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 Ligue 1. B\u00e0i h\u1ecdc x\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e1u \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap HLV Genesio quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u01a1n trong vi\u1ec7c n\u00e2ng cao th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Groupama m\u00f9a n\u00e0y gi\u00fap cho Lyon c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1i \u01b0u \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh; c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh s\u00f2ng ph\u1eb3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng Marseille, Monaco hay PSG cho 1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong Top 3. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00f3n ti\u1ebfp Amiens t\u1ed1i nay, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Fekir kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t v\u00ec t\u1eadp trung mu\u1ed9n sau World Cup, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Anthony Lopes th\u1ef1c thi n\u1ed1t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng trong \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t treo gi\u00f2 3 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i Ligue 1 \u1edf cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. N\u1ebfu Fekir kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u, Memphis Depay s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn vai tr\u00f2 h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Bertrand Traore v\u00e0 Martin Terrier.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 v\u1eady, Lyon \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu chu\u1ed7i 6 tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG. M\u00e3nh s\u01b0 c\u0169ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ghi t\u1eeb 3 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean \u1edf chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn n\u00f3i tr\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc Amiens. V\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n m\u00ecnh, Amiens l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ligue 1 thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu \u00edt nh\u1ea5t h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u 5 tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt 4-3-3 sau khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 sung ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Juan Ferney Otero trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. C\u00f3 v\u1ebb, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 c\u1ea3 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1eabn \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, Lyon s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN<br>\r\nTheo k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Lyon th\u1eafng 12, h\u00f2a 1, thua 7 \u1edf 20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t; Amiens th\u1eafng 11, h\u00f2a 1, thua 8 \u1edf 20 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\nTr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, Lyon th\u1eafng 10, h\u00f2a 1, thua 9 \u1edf 20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y theo k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<br>\r\nTr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch, Amiens th\u1eafng 10, thua 10 \u1edf 20 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua theo k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T<br>\r\nL\u01b0\u1edbi rung cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1<br>\r\n4/5 cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i, c\u1ea3 6 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Lyon v\u00e0 7 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a Amiens c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1eeb ph\u00fat 21-45. Ngo\u00e0i ra, 6/8 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Amiens c\u0169ng ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1edbi rung 25 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Bongdaplus.vn<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5384","checkdouble":"194305"},{"date":"10:57 12/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Frankfurt vs Bayern Munich 01h30 ng\u00e0y 13/8 (Si\u00eau c\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u1ee9c","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/12/nhan-dinh-frankfurt-vs-bayern-munich-01h30-ngay-138-sieu-cup-duc-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Frankfurt vs Bayern Munich l\u00fac 01h30 ng\u00e0y 13/8 (Si\u00eau c\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Frankfurt vs Bayern Munich 01h30 ng\u00e0y 138 Si\u00eau c\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Frankfurt vs Bayern Munich 01h30 ng\u00e0y 138 Si\u00eau c\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/Frankfurt-vs-Bayern-Munich.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Frankfurt vs Bayern Munich</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span>Frankfurt vs Bayern Munich: 0-2<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 tinh th\u1ea7n l\u00ean cao, Bayern Munich c\u00f2n c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec3u bi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a HLV Niko Kovac v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Frankfurt. Qua \u0111\u00e2y, Frankfurt nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ng\u1eadm ng\u00f9i d\u00e2ng c\u00fap cho H\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u2026<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1i t\u00ean Niko Kovac \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c 2018 gi\u1eefa Eintracht Frankfurt v\u00e0 Bayern Munich di\u1ec5n ra. Ch\u00ednh Kovac \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Frankfurt \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Bayern Munich v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft C\u00fap Qu\u1ed1c gia \u0110\u1ee9c m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc di\u1ec5n ra h\u00f4m 20/05/2018. C\u0169ng nh\u1edd nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c BL\u0110 Bayern Munich tin t\u01b0\u1edfng trao quy\u1ec1n HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thay th\u1ebf ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m Jupp Heynckes. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c n\u1eafm r\u00f5 n\u1ed9i t\u00ecnh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec3u bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Frankfurt, Kovac c\u00f9ng \u00ea k\u00edp c\u1ed9ng s\u1ef1 trong BHL Bayern Munich ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u1edf tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau C\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c n\u0103m nay. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 Bayern Munich \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t b\u1eb1ng th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 s\u00e1t n\u00fat 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 nh\u1eb1n l\u00e0 Man United \u1edf tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1eeba qua. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Frankfurt d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Adi Huetter \u0111ang g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 h\u01a1n, Frankfurt \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n l\u00e0 SPAL v\u00e0 Empoli. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, H\u00f9m x\u00e1m c\u00f2n chi\u1ebfm \u01b0u th\u1ebf h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e0nh danh nh\u01b0 Lewandowski, Ribery, Mueller hay Robben\u2026 <br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i m\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 c\u0169ng \u0111ang \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Bayern Munich tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Frankfurt. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 h\u00f3a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Bayern Munich \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i t\u1edbi 53 tr\u1eadn sau 95 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Frankfurt t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi nay. Sau 6 l\u1ea7n \u0111o\u1ea1t Si\u00eau C\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c (1987, 1990, 2010, 2012, 2016, 2017), Bayern Munich r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd \u0111em v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Si\u00eau C\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 7 sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Eintracht Frankfurt. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN XUNG QUANH<br>\r\n- Theo k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Frankfurt thua 6/8 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Bayern Munich th\u1eafng 6/10 tr\u1eadn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n- B\u1ea3ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u1edf 25 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i 4/7 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a Frankfurt v\u00e0 4/6 tr\u1eadn m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T<br>\r\nCh\u1eb5n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng<br>\r\n5/7 tr\u1eadn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Frankfurt v\u00e0 5/8 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 ch\u1eb5n. Tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 chia h\u1ebft cho 2. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5383","checkdouble":"194303"},{"date":"10:16 12/08","title":"Sevilla t\u1ed1 Barca \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u00ean v\u1ecb t\u1ea1i Si\u00eau c\u00fap TBN","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/12/sevilla-to-cao-barca-truoc-sieu-cup-tay-ban-nha.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sevilla t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o Barca tr\u01b0\u1edbc Si\u00eau c\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Andalusia tin r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed b\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Barcelona th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Lu\u1eadt m\u1edbi c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho Barca</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m Si\u00eau c\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha (RFEF) \u0111\u00e3 ra lu\u1eadt Sevilla v\u00e0 Barcelona kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, thay v\u00ec ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o s\u00e2n 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngo\u00e0i Li\u00ean minh ch\u00e2u \u00c2u (EU), hai \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ef1 do l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 \u1edf m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n cho Barca, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1ed9 ba ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nam M\u1ef9 bao g\u1ed3m Arthur, Malcom (Brazil) v\u00e0 Arturo Vidal (Chile). \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh cho Sevilla. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Andalusia \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c RFEF thay \u0111\u1ed5i lu\u1eadt Si\u00eau c\u00fap TBN t\u1eeb 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 1 v\u00e0 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i m\u00e0 c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 n\u0103m nay l\u00e0 t\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Tangier, Ma-R\u1ed1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sevilla t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o Barca tr\u01b0\u1edbc Si\u00eau c\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sevilla t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o Barca tr\u01b0\u1edbc Si\u00eau c\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/sevilla-to-cao-barca-truoc-sieu-cup-tay-ban-nha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ph\u00eda Sevilla t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o Barca tr\u01b0\u1edbc Si\u00eau c\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nSevilla ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Sevilla t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o Barca tr\u01b0\u1edbc Si\u00eau c\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha. H\u1ecd \u0111\u0103ng m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Twitter v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 7, th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 quan ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. \u201cSevilla FC r\u1ea5t ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a RFEF 24 gi\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Si\u00eau c\u00fap\u201d, h\u1ecd vi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cLu\u1eadt m\u1edbi cho ph\u00e9p nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng thu\u1ed9c EU nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 trong th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u1ec1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 18/19 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p ph\u00e9p, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ngo\u1ea1i l\u1ec7.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn ph\u00e1p l\u00fd c\u1ee7a CLB \u0111ang xem x\u00e9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y. N\u1ebfu FC Barcelona mang m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi h\u01a1n 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng thu\u1ed9c EU, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf cho m\u1ed9t l\u00e1 \u0111\u01a1n khi\u1ebfu n\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea1m lu\u1eadt trong \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a Sevilla c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a. Theo th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Philippe Coutinho d\u00f9 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil song \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed9 chi\u1ebfu B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha th\u00f4ng qua v\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho ph\u00e9p Barca s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea3 Arthur, Malcom v\u00e0 Vidal tr\u01b0\u1edbc Sevilla.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Barcelona tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nhan-dinh-sevilla-vs-barca-3h-ngay-138-co-messi-la-co-tat-ca-180-194294.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Sevilla vs Barca (3h ng\u00e0y 13/8): C\u00f3 Messi l\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-van-nuoi-hy-vong-so-huu-pogba-180-194194.html\">Barca v\u1eabn nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu sao kh\u1ee7ng MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/paul-pogba-hanh-phuc-tai-mu-172-194152.html\">Ph\u1ea3i \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U, Pogba c\u00f3 c\u00f2n h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bo-doi-barcelona-noi-gi-sau-khi-cap-ben-nuoc-anh-172-194149.html\">B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Barcelona n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5382","checkdouble":"194300"},{"date":"09:23 12/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool vs West Ham (19h30 ng\u00e0y 12/8): Tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb b\u1ed9i chi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/nhan-dinh-liverpool-vs-west-ham-19h30-ngay-128-tran-chien-cua-nhung-ke-boi-chi.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ngay trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n, Liverpool s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0u tham v\u1ecdng kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 West Ham tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 The Klopp t\u1ecf r\u00f5 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \"tranh b\u00e1\" \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eed th\u00e1ch t\u1eeb West Ham<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8, West Ham chi ra \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n 90 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 11 t\u00e2n binh. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n b\u1ecf nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n ra \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u00f4ng l\u1edbn trong nh\u00f3m Big Six. Ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb Chelsea v\u00e0 Liverpool, c\u1ea3 b\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i trong nh\u00f3m top 6 \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng chi nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n b\u1eb1ng West Ham trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Manuel Pellegrini nhan dinh Liverpool vs West Ham la co hoi de doi bong cua ong the hien tham vong.\" title=\"Manuel Pellegrini nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool vs West Ham l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tham v\u1ecdng.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/pellegrini.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Manuel Pellegrini nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool vs West Ham l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tham v\u1ecdng.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e2n HLV Manuel Pellegrini kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh West Ham \u0111ang th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n m\u1edbi nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u1eb7t n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 ngay t\u1eeb h\u00e8 n\u00e0y: &quot;Khi th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn v\u1edbi ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ed r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n. H\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 ti\u1ec1n b\u1ea1c cho nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean, vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn bao gi\u1edd c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Gi\u1edd th\u00ec t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn, hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf m\u1ed7i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf t\u00ecm ra \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ee7a HLV Manuel Pellegrini c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u1edbi Liverpool. Th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t, West Ham \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Th\u1ee9 hai, HLV Pellegrini s\u1ebd d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho Liverpool ngay trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cac chuyen gia nhan dinh Liverpool vs West Ham la thach thuc nhung cung la co hoi chung minh ban than cua ca hai doi.\" title=\"C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool vs West Ham l\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ch\u1ee9ng minh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/liver.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool vs West Ham l\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ch\u1ee9ng minh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ee7a HLV Pellegrini c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 con dao hai l\u01b0\u1ee1i v\u1edbi West Ham. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn, West Ham s\u1ebd r\u01a1i v\u00e0o c\u00e1i b\u1eaby Jurgen Klopp gi\u0103ng ra. Ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Liverpool lu\u00f4n \u1ea9n ch\u1ee9a m\u1ed1i nguy hi\u1ec3m ti\u1ec1m t\u00e0ng khi Jurgen Klopp v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 Salah - Firmino - Sadio Mane, ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 th\u00eam s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Shaqiri.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 West Ham c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u nhau tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c b\u00e0i chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a HLV Pellegrini c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Liverpool khai th\u00e1c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh Liverpool<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi Jurgen Klopp n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n t\u1ea1i Liverpool, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 c\u1ea3ng lu\u00f4n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u1eebng b\u1eebng s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng. C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u00fac h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng v\u00f9i d\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng khi b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m d\u1eabn t\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jurgen Klopp lo lang khi Liverpool khung hoang hang thu truoc tran mo man Premier League 2018-19.\" title=\"Jurgen Klopp lo l\u1eafng khi Liverpool kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League 2018-19.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/klopp-chua-dam-dat-liverpool-ngang-hang-man-city.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Jurgen Klopp lo l\u1eafng khi Liverpool kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League 2018-19.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Liverpool l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i chi nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Premier League \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Jurgen Klopp hi\u1ec3u \u00f4ng c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 sau hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i r\u01b0\u1ee1i tr\u1eafng tay c\u00f9ng Liverpool. S\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o The Klopp \u0111ang r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Liverpool ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn \u0111\u00e3 hi\u1ec3u \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Klopp, c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi nhau tr\u00ean s\u00e2n ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh. Klopp c\u0169ng b\u1ed5 sung nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 Liverpool c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m t\u1ef1 b\u1eafn v\u00e0o ch\u00e2n trong nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft, l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool l\u00fac n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu khi Klopp \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tranh ch\u1ea5p v\u00e0o khu trung tuy\u1ebfn g\u1ed3m Naby Keita v\u00e0 Fabinho. M\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00ed nh\u01b0 &quot;Messi trong khung g\u1ed7&quot; l\u00e0 Alisson \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf sai l\u1ea7m. \u00d4ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng n\u1eefa l\u00e0 Shaqiri.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Liverpool vs West Ham\" title=\"Preview Liverpool vs West Ham\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/nhan-dinh-liverpool-vs-west-ham-19h30-ngay-128-tran-chien-cua-nhung-ke-boi-chi.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool vs West Ham - cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb b\u1ed9i chi.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Anfield s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Jurgen Klopp ch\u1ee9ng minh h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. C\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng Klopp \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Liverpool v\u1edbi b\u1ed1n b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 hay ch\u01b0a?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn:</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* Liverpool th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 ba tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t g\u1eb7p West Ham t\u1ea1i Premier League, \u0111\u1ec1u ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1n b\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* West Ham l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 thua Liverpool nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Premier League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y (61 l\u1ea7n, b\u1eb1ng Everton).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* West Ham ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 1 l\u1ea7n trong s\u1ed1 45 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Anfield trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Anh (h\u00f2a 12, thua 32). \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 3-0 v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 8/2015.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* West Ham thua trong 11 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* Sadio Mane \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o b\u1ed1n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong ba tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p West Ham t\u1ea1i Premier League (1 b\u00e0n, 3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u00f4ng tin l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng:</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Liverpool: </strong>Alex Oxlade Chamberlain, Ragnar Klavan ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng - Dejan Lovren, Joseph Gomez, Joel Matip, Fabinho, James Milner ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc ra s\u00e2n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>West Ham:</strong> Winston Reid, Manuel Lanzini, Andy Carroll ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng - Carlos Sanchez, Lucas Perez, Andriy Yarmolenko ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc ra s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Liverpool vs West Ham (19h30 ng\u00e0y 12/8):</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Liverpool (4-3-3):</strong> 13.Alisson - 66.Alexander-Arnold, 12. Joe Gomez, 4.Van Dijk, 26.A.Robertson - 5.Wijnaldum, 14.Henderson, 8.Naby Keita - 10.Mane, 9.Firmino, 11.Salah</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>West Ham (4-3-3): </strong>1.Fabianski - 5.Zabaleta, 23.Diop, 21.Ogbonna, 3.Cresswell - 14.Obiang, 16.Noble, 19.Wilshere - 20.Yarmolenko, 8.Anderson, 7.Arnautovic</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1:</strong> Liverpool 4-2 West Ham<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Liverpool m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bom-tan-cua-liverpool-xoay-sau-vao-noi-dau-cua-mu-172-194284.html\">Bom t\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a Liverpool xo\u00e1y s\u00e2u v\u00e0o n\u1ed7i \u0111au c\u1ee7a MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-klopp-tu-choi-ban-hang-thai-cho-newcastle-172-194271.html\">HLV Klopp t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i cho Newcastle</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alisson-quyet-chung-to-gia-tri-cua-mot-bom-tan-172-194269.html\">Alisson quy\u1ebft ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t bom t\u1ea5n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/them-mot-tien-dao-sap-chia-tay-liverpool-172-194245.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o s\u1eafp chia tay Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-van-cay-cu-va-khang-dinh-ramos-la-noi-si-nhuc-172-194241.html\">Klopp v\u1eabn cay c\u00fa v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ramos l\u00e0 n\u1ed7i s\u1ec9 nh\u1ee5c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-klopp-noi-ve-chuyen-nhuong-liverpool-he-2018-172-194217.html\">S\u1eafm s\u1eeda xong xu\u00f4i, gi\u1edd Klopp mu\u1ed1n d\u1ecdn d\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Liverpool</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ea1t (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5381","checkdouble":"194296"},{"date":"09:45 12/08","title":"T\u1ea1i sao Pogba ch\u01b0a c\u00f4ng khai mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/3/paul-pogba-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-cua-minh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Paul Pogba l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i ra v\u00ed nh\u01b0 vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Man United hay kh\u00f4ng, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng s\u1ebd b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPogba tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPaul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua World Cup 2018 kh\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Croatia 4-2, n\u01a1i anh c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Pogba ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho M.U trong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch 2018/19. \u1ede tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League v\u1edbi Leicester City, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Juventus \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. Anh c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong su\u1ed1t 90 ph\u00fat d\u00f9 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n 4 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paul Pogba l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Paul Pogba l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/3/paul-pogba-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-cua-minh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Paul Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nL\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u00e0y, c\u00f3 tin Barcelona v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Juventus r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Paul Pogba. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tin \u0111\u1ed3n ch\u00ednh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i b\u1edfi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\u1ec1m vui t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford. Anh v\u00e0i l\u1ea7n h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch t\u1eeb HLV Jose Mourinho, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Champions League v\u1edbi Sevilla.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eeb gi\u1edd t\u1edbi h\u1ebft th\u00e1ng 8, Pogba v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi M.U. Chi\u1ec1u mua c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c CLB n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i song h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 cho c\u00e1c CLB n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c nh\u1eefng Barca hay Juventus v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u1edf h\u1eefu Pogba.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-gay-soc-pogba-la-mot-con-quai-thu-172-194225.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/mourinho-gay-soc-pogba-la-mot-con-quai-thu.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-gay-soc-pogba-la-mot-con-quai-thu-172-194225.html\">Mourinho g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c: \u201cPogba l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t con qu\u00e1i th\u00fa\u201d</span><br>\r\n<span>Paul Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 c\u1ee7a M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y. HLV Jose Mourinho kh\u00f4ng...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u1eb7t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i M.U hay kh\u00f4ng, Paul Pogba l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh: \u201cC\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t. Khi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi tin t\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1ea1n v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong \u0111\u1ea7u, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 r\u1ea1n n\u1ee9t v\u1edbi HLV Mourinho, Pogba c\u0169ng \u0111\u0103ng m\u1ed9t d\u00f2ng tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Instagram: \u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh v\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra\u201d, anh vi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cac-muc-tieu-tu-choi-mu-la-loi-cua-mourinho-172-194161.html\">C\u00e1c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i M.U l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a Mourinho</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cac-muc-tieu-tu-choi-mu-la-loi-cua-mourinho-172-194161.html\">C\u00e1c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i M.U l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a Mourinho</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hai-huoc-ai-bao-mu-khong-co-tan-binh-nao-mua-he-nay-172-194160.html\">H\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc: Ai b\u1ea3o M.U kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/paul-pogba-hanh-phuc-tai-mu-172-194152.html\">Ph\u1ea3i \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U, Pogba c\u00f3 c\u00f2n h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5380","checkdouble":"194297"},{"date":"09:56 12/08","title":"Sarri ch\u1ec9 ra 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Huddersfield","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/sarri-chi-ra-2-diem-yeu-cua-chelsea-o-tran-gap-huddersfield.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Maurizio Sarri v\u1eeba ch\u1ec9 ra 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n Chelsea c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng Huddersfield.</h2><h2>Chelsea th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm Huddersfield\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sarri\" title=\"Sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/sarri-chi-ra-2-diem-yeu-cua-chelsea-o-tran-gap-huddersfield.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Sarri ch\u01b0a h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng sau tr\u1eadn Huddersfield vs Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf Premier League. Nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a N&rsquo;golo Kante, Jorginho v\u00e0 Pedro \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap The Blues th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 3-0 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Huddersfield.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 1 th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t \u00edt th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh The Blues. C\u0169ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi ch\u00e2n \u01b0\u1edbt ch\u00e2n r\u00e1o c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<h2>Sarri ch\u01b0a h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Sarri s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi Arsenal. V\u00e0 thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Chelsea th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u00f4ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i Sarri-ball nh\u01b0 m\u00ecnh mong mu\u1ed1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 \u00e1p s\u00e1t v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i lu\u00e2n chuy\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng nhanh h\u01a1n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u00e0o hi\u1ec7p hai khi c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian x\u1eed l\u00fd h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang \u1edf m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c th\u00ec ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i may m\u1eafn v\u00ec b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c 1 tr\u1eadn m\u1ed7i tu\u1ea7n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n trong th\u00e1ng n\u00e0y. Khi \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00ec m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 l\u1ea1i kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 trong th\u00e1ng n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng v\u1eeba qua v\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm \u0111i\u1ec3m. Hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. N\u1ebfu c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1, c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ec5 v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 trong 15 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean khi b\u1ecb ng\u1ee3p tr\u01b0\u1edbc Huddersfield. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u1ef1ng trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Huddersfield \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5m m\u1ec7t v\u00e0o hi\u1ec7p hai&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVideo t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn Huddersfield vs Chelsea:\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278917\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/08/11/huddersfield-chelsea.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"340\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Huddersfield vs Chelsea:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-huddersfield-03-chelsea-172-194286.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Huddersfield 0-3 Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-ra-quan-suon-se-cua-chelsea-172-194281.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5379","checkdouble":"194299"},{"date":"10:59 12/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec1u g\u00ec khi\u1ebfn Guardiola c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Man City?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/12/hlv-pep-guardiola-phat-bieu-ve-doi-hinh-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Pep Guardiola ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Man City. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i xoay v\u00f2ng nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 khi\u1ebfn \u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Man City d\u1ed3i d\u00e0o nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMan City \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, HLV Pep Guardiola s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t nh\u01b0 Vincent Kompany v\u00e0 Nicolas Otamendi ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 John Stones v\u00e0 Aymeric Laporte v\u1eabn ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5, gi\u00fap Man City gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng cho m\u1ed9t Man City r\u1ea5t d\u1ed3i d\u00e0o nh\u00e2n l\u1ef1c v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam Riyad Mahrez v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i 1 khi\u1ebfn cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Pep Guardiola ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Pep Guardiola ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/HLV-Pep-Guardiola-phat-bieu-ve-doi-hinh-Man-City-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Man City ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t h\u00f9ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Guardiola c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u nh\u01b0 Man City l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a bi\u1ebft bao \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi ri\u00eang Pep Guardiola, \u00f4ng l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m x\u00fac kh\u00e1c. \u201cC\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng\u201d, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTh\u1eadt kh\u00f3 khi b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u1ed7i \u0111au c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. C\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. M\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV v\u00e0 s\u1ebd bi\u1ebft ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Guardiola\" title=\"HLV Guardiola\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/hlv-pep-guardiola-phat-bieu-ve-doi-hinh-man-city.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV\u00a0Guardiola ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea1nh tranh \u1edf 4 \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 trung v\u1ec7 gi\u1ecfi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao nh\u1ea5t. H\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh l\u1eabn nhau v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn c\u00e1c quy t\u1eafc c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. H\u00f4m nay c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0ng ng\u00e0y mai b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 h\u1ecd lu\u00f4n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ed1i nay, v\u00e0o l\u00fac 22h, Man City s\u1ebd l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Arsenal t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man City tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-arsenal-vs-man-city-22h-ngay-128-khac-biet-o-nen-tang-172-194293.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Arsenal vs Man City (22h ng\u00e0y 12/8): Kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/unai-emery-da-chon-ra-thu-mon-bat-chinh-truoc-man-city-172-194239.html\">Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn ra th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-guardiola-ung-ho-chelsea-pha-ky-luc-chuyen-nhuong-the-gioi-vi-thu-mon-kepa-172-194215.html\">Pep Guardiola \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Chelsea vung ti\u1ec1n v\u00ec th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-guardiola-man-city-het-tien-mua-cau-thu-roi-172-194212.html\">Pep Guardiola: \u201cMan City h\u1ebft ti\u1ec1n mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ed3i!\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-chua-dam-dat-liverpool-ngang-hang-man-city-172-194204.html\">Klopp ch\u01b0a d\u00e1m \u0111\u1eb7t Liverpool ngang h\u00e0ng Man City</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5378","checkdouble":"194301"},{"date":"08:38 12/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Sevilla vs Barca (3h ng\u00e0y 13/8): C\u00f3 Messi l\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/12/nhan-dinh-sevilla-vs-barca-3h-ngay-138-co-messi-la-co-tat-ca.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barcelona m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 si\u00eau sao Lionel Messi. Nh\u01b0ng khi s\u1ed1 10 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca giao h\u1eefu th\u1ea5t b\u00e1t</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u1ea3i qua 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, Barcelona \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c. Vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Tottenham sau lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem tr\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede 2 tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, Barca to\u00e0n thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc AS Roma v\u00e0 AC Milan. 3 tr\u1eadn kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u00f4i qua, vi\u1ec7c Blaugrana ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 b\u00e0n c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng trong khi con s\u1ed1 7 b\u00e0n thua t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u01a1i g\u1eddn g\u1ee3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Sevilla vs Barca (3h ng\u00e0y 138) C\u00f3 Messi l\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Sevilla vs Barca (3h ng\u00e0y 138) C\u00f3 Messi l\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/Nhan-dinh-Sevilla-vs-Barca-(3h-ngay-138)-Co-Messi-la-co-tat-ca-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barca kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i IC\u00a0Cup</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e2n binh 35 tri\u1ec7u Euro, Clement Lenglet v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp c\u00f9ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Barca. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, do Gerard Pique v\u00e0 Samuel Umtiti kh\u00f4ng sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Ernesto Valverde c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c ch\u01a1i \u1ed5n h\u01a1n c\u1ea1nh Lenglet.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Barca lu\u00f4n trong t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng h\u1ed7n lo\u1ea1n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0o. \u1ede ph\u00eda tr\u00ean, c\u00e1c m\u0169i c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p n\u1ed5i s\u1ef1 s\u01a1 h\u1edf n\u01a1i h\u1eadu ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh n\u1eb1m \u1edf vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd thi\u1ebfu \u0111i nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 Luis Suarez, Philippe Coutinho v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Lionel Messi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Sevilla vs Barca (3h ng\u00e0y 138) C\u00f3 Messi l\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Sevilla vs Barca (3h ng\u00e0y 138) C\u00f3 Messi l\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/Nhan-dinh-Sevilla-vs-Barca-(3h-ngay-138)-Co-Messi-la-co-tat-ca-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Blaugrana l\u00fac n\u00e0y kh\u00e1 l\u1ecfng l\u1ebbo</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nS\u1ebd kh\u00e1c \u1edf Si\u00eau c\u00fap</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e2y gi\u1edd, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta m\u1edbi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Barca ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o Lionel Messi. Su\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua, d\u00f9 c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0 \u0111i, Blaugrana v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina. Ch\u1ec9 khi c\u00f3 anh, l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd m\u1edbi th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 m\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0, nhu\u1ea7n nhuy\u1ec5n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ee3p l\u00fd n\u1ebfu bi\u1ebft Barca v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i xung quanh Messi su\u1ed1t m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ee9t \u0111i ch\u1edbp nho\u00e1ng c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng pha x\u1eed l\u00fd b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin n\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 31 tu\u1ed5i lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Blaugrana \u0111\u1ea3o ng\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Sevilla vs Barca (3h ng\u00e0y 138) C\u00f3 Messi l\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Sevilla vs Barca (3h ng\u00e0y 138) C\u00f3 Messi l\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/4/Nhan-dinh-Sevilla-vs-Barca-(3h-ngay-138)-Co-Messi-la-co-tat-ca-hinh-anh-3.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">S\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Suarez v\u00e0 Messi s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t h\u1eefu \u00edch cho Barcs</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0o m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y th\u0103ng hoa, Barca c\u00f3 Messi s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ch\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt. \u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc thi\u00ean t\u00e0i c\u1ee7a Leo, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a anh v\u1eabn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng sau c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Sevilla vs Barca c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf qua chi ti\u1ebft n\u00e0y. D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, Messi, Suarez r\u1ed3i Coutinho \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1ebd g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Ibn Batouta, Ma-R\u1ed1c. Ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0a Si\u00eau c\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha ra n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i, ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do Barca kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea5t qu\u00e2n l\u00e2u h\u01a1n. H\u1ecd c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u00e0m b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1p cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, x\u00f3a \u0111i nh\u1eefng u \u00e1m t\u1ea1i International Champions Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/malcom-chia-khoa-cho-su-linh-hoat-cua-barcelona-180-192062.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/malcom-chia-khoa-cho-su-linh-hoat-cua-barcelona.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/malcom-chia-khoa-cho-su-linh-hoat-cua-barcelona-180-192062.html\">Malcom \u2013 Ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a cho s\u1ef1 linh ho\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Barcelona</span><br>\r\n<span>\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eadt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft AS Roma. Nh\u01b0ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, Barca s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Malcom nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nSevilla kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng t\u1ea1o b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSevilla nh\u01b0 m\u1ecdi n\u0103m v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. H\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 6 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ra \u0111i trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 Lenglet t\u1edbi ch\u00ednh Barca r\u1ed3i Joaquin Correa, Guido Pizarro, David Soria, Juan Munoz v\u00e0 Sergio Rico. \u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Andalusia \u0111\u00f3n v\u1ec1 6 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t Ibrahim Amadou (t\u1eeb Lille), Joris Gnagnon (Rennes), Aleix Vidal (Barca), Tomas Vaclik (Basel), Roque Mesa (Swansea) r\u1ed3i Sergi G\u00f3mez (Celta Vigo) n\u1ed1i g\u00f3t nhau t\u1edbi Sevilla. Tr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng do HLV Pablo Mach\u00edn d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u00e3 chi 57 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Sevilla vs Barca\" title=\"Preview Sevilla vs Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/Preview-Sevilla-vs-Barca.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Sevilla vs Barca 3h ng\u00e0y 13/8</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, Sevilla \u0111\u00e3 thu v\u1ec1 63,5 tri\u1ec7u Euro ti\u1ec1n b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, ch\u01b0a h\u1eb3n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, vi\u1ec7c thu l\u1eddi t\u1eeb chi\u1ec1u mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 cho th\u1ea5y t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng \u201ccon bu\u00f4n\u201d v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Sevilla c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i l\u1edbn. Th\u00eam n\u1eefa, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi. Tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac Sevilla \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 sung m\u00e3n v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9. H\u1ecd m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng Europa League v\u1edbi Zalgiris Vilnius \u0111\u00eam th\u1ee9 5 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang 3 ng\u00e0y sau ph\u1ea3i bay t\u1edbi Ma-R\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e1 Si\u00eau c\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u01b0u th\u1ebf \u0111ang thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Barca. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Messi c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nSevilla (3-4-3):</strong> 13.Vaclik - 24.Gnagnon, 4.Kjaer, 25.Mercado - 16.Navas, 7.Mesa, 10.Banega, 18.Escudero - 17.Sarabia, 9.Ben Yedder, 8.Nolito.<br>\r\n<strong>Barcelona (4-3-3):</strong> 1.Stegen - 20.Roberto, 3.Pique, 15.Lenglet, 18.Alba - 14.Coutinho, 5.Busquets, 4.Arthur - 10.Messi, 9.Su\u00e1rez, 26.Malcom.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: Barcelona th\u1eafng 3-1<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Sevilla vs Barca\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Sevilla vs Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/Sevilla-vs-Barca-(3-4-3-vs-4-3-3).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Sevilla vs Barca</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5377","checkdouble":"194294"},{"date":"07:13 12/08","title":"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Huddersfield 0-3 Chelsea: M\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Sarri","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/du-am-huddersfield-03-chelsea-man-ra-quan-suon-se-cua-sarri.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00f3 l\u1ebd v\u1edbi ngay c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c C\u0110V The Blues c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng mong ch\u1edd m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng d\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Huddersfield vs Chelsea t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1 gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Khi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e1 may m\u1eafn khi gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady, b\u1edfi th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi Kante v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, b\u1edfi Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 b\u1ebf t\u1eafc trong nh\u1eefng \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap The Blues r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u1ee9 ngh\u0129 m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a bom t\u1ea5n Kepa chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb rung l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn n\u01a1i. V\u00e0 sau khi d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 1 b\u00e0n, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n di\u1ec5n ra c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 su\u00f4n s\u1ebb v\u1edbi Chelsea, h\u1ecd kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7p 1 v\u1edbi c\u00fa s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh c\u1ee7a Jorginho.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Huddersfield vs Chelsea M\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a Sarri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Huddersfield vs Chelsea M\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a Sarri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Du-am-Huddersfield-vs-Chelsea-Man-ra-mat-hoan-hao-cua-Sarri-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7p 2, ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u, b\u1edfi Chelsea n\u1eafm gi\u1eef l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1. H\u1ecd t\u1ea1o ra th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u01a1n, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 kh\u00e1 b\u00ecnh th\u1ea3n trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t l\u00ean b\u00f3ng. B\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 3-0 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t pha ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a &ldquo;t\u00e2n binh&rdquo; Eden Hazard.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t nh\u01b0 Kante, Hazard, nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao b\u1ecb qu\u00ean l\u00e3ng nh\u01b0 Pedro, \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00e2n binh Jorginho hay th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Kepa Arrizabalaga &ndash; t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi HLV Sarri. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t, n\u1ebfu so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 London t\u1ea1o ra trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pedro Hazard\" title=\"Pedro Hazard\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/ped.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pedro v\u00e0 Hazard t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 3 cho Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi Sarriball</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00e1ng khen nh\u1ea5t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 The Blues. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f2n l\u00e0 tuy\u1ebfn tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y m\u1edbi. Kepa tuy kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m, nh\u01b0ng nh\u00ecn chung th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng pha c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin t\u1eeb th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 23 tu\u1ed5i, khi anh tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00f3ng cho nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7. Ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3, Marcos Alonso d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 th\u00edch h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u1edbi, khi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c d\u00e2ng l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u1ea1o ra qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng khi d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m d\u1ed9i x\u00e0 ngang.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 Rudiger &ndash; Luiz, c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Sarri trao ni\u1ec1m tin trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua. Trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao vai tr\u00f2 l\u1edbn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu t\u1eeb h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec John Stones th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong Pep-team, David Luiz s\u1edf h\u1eefu 93 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n trong tr\u1eadn, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 &ldquo;vua chuy\u1ec1n&rdquo; Jorginho.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/chel.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Luiz (30) trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Huddersfield</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, N&rsquo;Golo Kante \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng l\u1ec7ch c\u00e1nh, thay v\u00ec ch\u1ec9 lo nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u00e0n qu\u00e9t tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. S\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00e0y ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ph\u00e1t huy t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng hi\u1ebfm hoi Kante ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. N\u00ean nh\u1edb, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p trong 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Premier League l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0&hellip; 1, 1 v\u00e0 1. Nh\u01b0ng ngay trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri, Kante \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi Sarriball, v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho. Anh kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Huddersfield, nh\u01b0ng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i v\u00e0o t\u00e2n binh 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb7t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi, n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Jorginho th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Chelsea s\u1ebd c\u00f2n kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u? \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean, The Blues v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 Mateo Kovacic v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a &ldquo;l\u00ean s\u00f3ng&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 trong d\u01b0 \u00e2m Huddersfield vs Chelsea, b\u1edfi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt Sarriball v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278917\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/08/11/huddersfield-chelsea.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"340\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-huddersfield-03-chelsea-172-194286.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-huddersfield-03-chelsea.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-huddersfield-03-chelsea-172-194286.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Huddersfield 0-3 Chelsea</span><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Huddersfield v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Huddersfield vs Chelsea v\u00f2ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-ra-quan-suon-se-cua-chelsea-172-194281.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-ra-quan-suon-se-cua-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-ra-quan-suon-se-cua-chelsea-172-194281.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Premier League c\u1ee7a Sarri \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Huddersfield vs Chelsea 0-3.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-con-so-biet-noi-sau-tran-huddersfield-vs-chelsea-172-194282.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/nhung-con-so-biet-noi-sau-tran-huddersfield-vs-chelsea.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-con-so-biet-noi-sau-tran-huddersfield-vs-chelsea-172-194282.html\">Nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 bi\u1ebft n\u00f3i sau tr\u1eadn Huddersfield vs Chelsea</span><br>\r\nM\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Huddersfield vs Chelsea t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5376","checkdouble":"194287"},{"date":"08:38 12/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Arsenal vs Man City (22h ng\u00e0y 12/8): Kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/11/nhan-dinh-arsenal-vs-man-city-22h-ngay-128-khac-biet-o-nen-tang.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Arsenal vs Man City hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb hai tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed1i l\u1eadp c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i. M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang \u0111\u1eb7t nh\u1eefng vi\u00ean g\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean x\u00e2y n\u00ean tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ec9 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ed7 m\u00e1y chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o. D\u1ef1a theo \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, Man City c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal ch\u1eadp ch\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i 22 n\u0103m c\u1ee7a Arsene Wenger t\u1ea1i Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18. C\u00e1i k\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1ng bu\u1ed3n khi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 6 t\u1ea1i Premier League v\u00e0 n\u0103m th\u1ee9 2 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 Champions League c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1c h\u1eadu n\u01a1i tri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nUnai Emery \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd &ldquo;hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i h\u00f3a&rdquo; Arsenal v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a h\u1ecd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn. chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. H\u1ecd th\u1eafng 4 trong s\u1ed1 5 tr\u1eadn kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 duy nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn thua Atletico Madrid sau lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Arsenal vs Man City (22h ng\u00e0y 128) Kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Arsenal vs Man City (22h ng\u00e0y 128) Kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/Nhan-dinh-Arsenal-vs-Man-City-(22h-ngay-128)-Khac-biet-o-nen-ta-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Arsenal c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u1edf Premier League kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u s\u1ebd l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00e1c. Emery h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 5 t\u00e2n binh bao g\u1ed3m Bernd Leno, Sokratis, Stephan Lichtsteiner, Lucas Torreira hay Matteo Guendouzi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Arsenal vs Man City v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 Champions League, kinh ph\u00ed mua s\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Arsenal ch\u1eadt h\u1eb9p v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng thu h\u00fat \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i. Nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean tr\u00ean ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Arsenal vs Man City\" title=\"Preview Arsenal vs Man City\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-1282018.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Arsenal vs Man City 22h ng\u00e0y 12/8</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 5 t\u00e2n binh Arsenal \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1edbi t\u1eeb b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1edbi. T\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp nhanh ch\u00f3ng. C\u1ea7n th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0i test \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng minh Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 &ldquo;l\u1ed9t x\u00e1c&rdquo; d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Emery.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Man City \u0111ang ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Man City \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c t\u1ea1i Premier League khi gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u1edbi tr\u00f2n 100 \u0111i\u1ec3m. H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam Ryiad Mahrez, tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Leicester \u0111\u0103ng quang n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh m\u00f9a 2015/16. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, m\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u1ed1 1 cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Aguero bo lo co hoi cua Man City\" title=\"Aguero bo lo co hoi cua Man City\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/Goc-Man-City-Khi-El-Kun-nhay-mua-duoi-anh-mat-troi-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Man City \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea t\u1ea1i Community Shield c\u00e0ng gi\u00fap Man City c\u00f3 th\u00eam s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 The Citizens c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu \u0111i c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Ederson, David Silva, Kevin De Bruyne ho\u1eb7c v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb nh\u01b0 Vincent Kompany, Nico Otamendi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Guardiola gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5m \u0111\u1eabm b\u00ean trong t\u1eebng th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Man City. D\u00f9 l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u1eabn s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ea1o n\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn. M\u00f4 h\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u00e0 HLV Guardiola mang t\u1edbi ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t tr\u1edf n\u00ean \u01b0u vi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 c\u00e0ng nguy hi\u1ec3m h\u01a1n khi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Man xanh r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed7i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, Sterling hay David Silva ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-02-man-city-pep-team-bao-tin-du-cho-nuoc-anh-172-193808.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/chelsea-02-man-city-pep-team-bao-tin-du-cho-nuoc-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-02-man-city-pep-team-bao-tin-du-cho-nuoc-anh-172-193808.html\">Chelsea 0-2 Man City: &ldquo;Pep team&rdquo; b\u00e1o tin d\u1eef cho n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh</span><br>\r\n<span>Man City \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 mu\u1ed1n h\u1ea1 b\u1ec7 h\u1ecd. Tuy nhi\u00ean, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Chelsea 0-2 Man City \u0111\u1ea7y thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nKh\u00f3 kh\u0103n ch\u1edd \u0111\u00f3n Arsenal</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 may m\u1eafn nh\u01b0 Man City. Tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Emirates, h\u1ecd thi\u1ebfu nguy\u00ean c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i l\u00e0 Nacho Montreal v\u00e0 Sead Kolasinac. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 thay h\u1ecd l\u00e0 Ainsley Maitland-Niles v\u1eeba non kinh nghi\u1ec7m, v\u1eeba kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m khai th\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Man City \u0111\u00eam ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt n\u00e0y. \u1ede c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i, m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Man City s\u1ebd quy t\u1ee5, t\u1eeb t\u00e2n binh Mahrez, ng\u00f4i sao De Bruyne cho t\u1edbi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Kyle Walker. Ch\u1ec9 1 trong s\u1ed1 h\u1ecd th\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee7 khi\u1ebfn cho Maitland-Niles kh\u1ed1n kh\u1ed5.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kolasinac\" title=\"Kolasinac\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/kolasinac-chan-thuong-nghi-10-tuan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Kolasinac v\u00e0 Montreal khi\u1ebfn Arsenal g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nEmery v\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u1ecdng kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu c\u1ee7a Guardiola. \u00d4ng ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha trong 10 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y (thua 6, h\u00f2a 4). M\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, Arsenal c\u0169ng l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 &ldquo;m\u1ed3i ngon&rdquo; c\u1ee7a Man City. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, h\u1ecd thua tan n\u00e1t \u1edf c\u1ea3 3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i Premier League, Arsenal th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 1-3 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch v\u00e0 0-3 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. T\u1ea1i chung k\u1ebft c\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng thua tr\u1eafng 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Wembley. C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t \u00edt y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Arsenal ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Emirates. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nArsenal (4-2-3-1):</strong> 19.Leno - 2.Beller\u00edn, 20.Mustafi, 5.Sokratis, 15.Maitland-Niles - 8.Ramsey, 11.Torreira - 7.Mkhitaryan, 10.Ozil, 14.Aubameyang - 9.Lacazette.<br>\r\n<strong>Man City (4-3-3):</strong> 31.Ederson - 2.Walker, 5.Stones, 14.Laporte, 22.Mendy - 17.Bruyne, 25.Fernandinho, 20.B.Silva - 26.Mahrez, 10.Aguero, 19.Sane.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: Man City th\u1eafng 2-1<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Arsenal vs Man City\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Arsenal vs Man City\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/Arsenal-vs-Man-City-(4-2-3-1-vs-4-3-3).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Arsenal vs Man City</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5375","checkdouble":"194293"},{"date":"19:37 11/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 11/08: Real c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng thay Kovacic","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-1108-real-co-tan-binh-45-trieu-bang-thay-kovacic.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 11/08.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng thay Kovacic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 1108 Real mua Thiago h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 1108 Real mua Thiago h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Diem-tin-Bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-1108-Real-mua-Thiago-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real chi 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Thiago Alcantara</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Onda Cero, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c s\u1edf h\u1eefu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Thiago Alcantara c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf cho Mateo Kovacic, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. Los Blancos \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 chi 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Cristiano Ronaldo d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cristiano Ronaldo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1edbi Juventus thi \u0111\u1ea5u khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia, CR7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi&nbsp;Real \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao anh d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Bayern Munich c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Ivan Rakitic</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau PSG v\u00e0 Monaco th\u00ec Bayern Munich c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ivan Rakitic c\u1ee7a Barca, song theo Mundo Deportivo \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 120 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rakitic\" title=\"Rakitic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/ngay-hom-nay-267.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bayern mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Rakitic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Klopp h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua s\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Liverpool</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jurgen Klopp kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi BL\u0110 Liverpool ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. The Kop \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ra 177 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Modric c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Inter Milan</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Calciomercato kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 BL\u0110 Real Madrid ra s\u1ee9c ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Luka Modric v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Inter Milan, song kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn mua Pogba</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd Sport, Barca \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c chi 130 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a M.U, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n t\u1eeb b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>David Luiz quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Sarri</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea muon doi David Luiz lay Giroud\" title=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i David Luiz l\u1ea5y Giroud\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/30/David-Luiz-phat-bieu-ve-HLV-Maurizio-Sarri-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>David Luiz mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Sarri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">David Luiz ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 HLV Maurizio Sarri, anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Alisson quy\u1ebft ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t &quot;bom t\u1ea5n&quot;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alisson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil t\u1ef1 tin ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Man City quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 Gundogam</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00eda Man City kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Gundogan v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o, Inter Milan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 40 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5374","checkdouble":"194270"}]}